{"tid":993623,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下宜家叫人捐錢果D係咪冇王管？","createTime":"2019-01-24T05:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T06:56:52.000Z","uid":149857,"like":18,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0d2bedcfc001963ee33c12cface64784dd3b46","tid":993623,"uid":149857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"果果都攞正牌有申請，仲會主動叫你影佢個牌<br />\n係太容易申請到定係假野但知道捐錢嘅人唔會特登check <br />\n咁岩岩番CUHK嘅時候係地鐵站到又一城交界有團體募款<br />\n我第一次就就咁行過左，第二次經過就比另一個阿姨攔住<br />\n<br />\n阿姨一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：捐錢幫下公公婆婆，你可以影宜張野架<br />\n阿姨二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：點解你咁似王祖藍<br />\n阿姨一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔會 你靚仔好多<br />\n我就準備搵幾蚊出黎<br />\n阿姨一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：捐多D啦 你睇下有人捐一百仲有人捐五百<br />\n我唯有拎張廿蚊出黎<br />\n阿姨一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如拎果張紅色嘅出黎 我見你有好多喎 捐一百蚊比公公婆婆買兩張棉被<br />\n（D錢老豆比我番學用 我一次過放曬係銀包）<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：.......<br />\n阿姨一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我睇你都負擔到啊<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：都唔洗啦<br />\n（入左20蚊落去急急腳走人）<br />\n<br />\n我從未聽過有人捐錢會叫人捐幾多，仲會講睇你個樣都負擔到之類嘅野<br />\n仲要話我似王祖藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲點會捐得多 我大約166中上樣<br />\n有冇吾城嘅弟兄姊妹都中左伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0348831f950932ce36c8a7a53f8c4334febd20f0","tid":993623,"uid":149857,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"吾城萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23471d87c9bccd14656a6a4fe1a2ae022b04645","tid":993623,"uid":56204,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"點解要捐錢比其他廢老<br />\n你屋企個兩件都未養得掂啦"},{"pid":"5e82ce0d0e72a6c7f4dc6b2043